tafsir[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,"Hino e sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, on ndaaroowo ma an Nulaaﾉ熔, o ndaartaama giiﾉ容 nder kono giiﾉ容 mak- ko feeﾃｱuﾉ容 ﾉ容n o ndaardat ma. E ko an waawata yi'innde on mo gite mun ﾉ登raa? Pellet a waawatah ﾉ蓉m. Ko wano non kadi a waawataa fewnugol waasuﾉ容 giiﾉ容-ﾉ兎rnde."
  10,44,"Pellet Alla Senike e tooﾃｱugol jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n. Kanko O tooﾃｱataa yeru abbere jarra. Si ko woni, ko kamﾉ兎 woni tooﾃｱirde ko'e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n naﾉ砥gol ﾉ容 e halkaare, sabu ko ﾉ兎 haﾉ橡妬tii kon e meere e townitaare."
  10,45,"ﾃ疎lnde Alla mooﾉ登yta yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka Darngal fii hasbugol ﾉ兎, wa'anay ﾉ兎 wa si ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ殿ano ka nguurndam maﾉ橡兎 aduna e cuﾉ預aji maﾉ橡兎, si wanaa saa'a gooto pet e ﾃｱalorma, hara yoga maﾉ橡兎 no anndita yoga, hooti ngol anndindirgol taﾆｴa hakkunde maﾉ橡兎 hakkee ko ﾉ兎 yi'i kon e fiyaaku laakara no tiiﾉ擁. Gomﾉ擁i ﾉ兎n fennuﾉ兎 kawral Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ngal ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ﾉ兎 sooyii, ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁naano immital ka aduna sakko ﾉ兎 hisa e sooyugol(perte)."
  10,46,"Si Men hollii ma an Nulaaﾉ熔, yoga e kon ko Men fodi ﾉ兎 e lepte ado a maayde maa nden, maa ﾉ蓉m Men ﾆｴettitu maa ado ﾉ蓉m, fow e mun, ko ka Amen woni ruttorde maﾉ橡兎 nden ﾃ疎lnde Darngal. Refti Alla ko ﾆｴellitiiﾉ熔 e kon ko ﾉ兎 gollata, huunde suuﾉ預aki Mo e ﾉ蓉m. O yoﾉ妬toyay ﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  10,47,"Hino woodani kala mofte yawtunooﾉ容 ﾉ容n Nulaaﾉ熔 imminaaﾉ熔 e maﾉ橡兎. Si tawii ko o nulaa kon yotti- yottike ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 fennii mo, ﾃｱaawirte hakkunde maﾉ橡兎 nuﾉ預l. Alla daﾉ溶ira mo ﾉ砥ral Makko ngal, O halkira ﾉ兎 nunﾉ預l Makko ngal. Kamﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 toonyetaake huunde e njoﾉ電i kuuﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  10,48,"ﾆ‘e heeferﾉ兎 no wi''ra townitagol e ﾉ妬icagol (dikkagol): ""Ko honnde tuma woni kon ko foduﾉ熔n men e lepte, si on laatike goonguﾉ兎 e kon nodditaﾉ熔n?"""
  10,49,"Maakan ﾉ兎 an Nulaaﾉ熔 : ""Mi waawanah hoore-am pooﾉ蓉gol lorra mo lorlira maa duﾃｱugol ﾉ蓉m e am, wanaa kadi nafa mo mi nafitorta. Ko honno mi nafirta goﾉ遼熔 goo maa mi lorra mo? Si wanaa hara ko muuyi ﾉ蓉m. Ko honno mi anndirta wirniiﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n? Hino woodani mofte kala ﾉ容 Alla kammbirani halakuyee, dumunna happaaﾉ熔 fii halkaare maﾉ橡兎 nden, gooto anndaa ﾉ蓉m si wanaa Alla. Si happu maﾉ橡兎 halkaare ngun hewtii, ﾉ兎 nennitantaake ﾉ蓉m waqtu woo, ﾉ兎 ardinantaake kadi""."
  10,50,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan ﾉ兎e hawjirﾉ兎 lepte : ""Habree lam, si lepte Alla ﾉ容n ardii on e waqtu kala jemma maa ﾃｱalorma, ko honﾉ蓉m woni ko hawjiranton ﾉ容e lepte?"""
  10,51,"E ko ﾉ殿awo nde lepte ﾉ容n ﾉ容 fodaﾉ熔n yani e mon gomﾉ擁nton, nokku ka gomﾉ擁nal nafatah wonkii ki gomﾉ擁naano ado ﾉ蓉m? E ko jooni non gomﾉ擁nton, gomﾉ擁i on laatinoke hawjirnooﾉ兎 lepte ﾉ容n ado hannde fennugol ﾉ容?"
  10,52,"Refti ﾉ殿awo nde ﾉ兎 naadaa ka lepte, ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬 yaltineede ton, ﾉ兎 wi'anee : ""Meeﾉ容e lepte luttude ﾉ容n laakara. Hara on yoﾉ兎te si wanaa kon ko gol- laynoﾉ熔n e keeferaaku e geddi?"""
  10,53,"ﾆ‘e sirkooﾉ兎 no habrino maa an Nulaaﾉ熔 : ""Hara ﾉ容e lepte ﾉ容 men fodaa ko goonga?"" Maakan ﾉ兎 : ""Eyyo, mi woondirii Alla ko ﾉ容 goonga. On wonaali laawotooﾉ兎 e majje""."
